title: Did Roy Moore receive 953 votes for Doug Jones 5,327 in a town of 1,867 registered voters?
subtitle: According to a popular Facebook rumor, the Alabama elections of December 2017 showed major irregularities in voting -- but the claim is "satisfaction."
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: Roy Moore obtained 953 votes and Doug Jones 5,327 -- in a town with only 1,867 registered voters.
